521
00:44:49,659 --> 00:44:52,880
[SPEAKER_04] i AI-a, ali sam iskreno više na strani AI-a.

522
00:44:52,880 --> 00:44:54,539
[SPEAKER_09] Više bi vjeroval o AI-u.

523
00:44:54,539 --> 00:44:59,699
[SPEAKER_09] Ok, zanimljivo, to što si rekao da, dakle, AI ipak ima u vidu neki tvoj život,

524
00:44:59,699 --> 00:45:03,920
[SPEAKER_09] ipak može, ako mu daš pristup, naravno, to će nam biti interesantno kasnije,

525
00:45:03,920 --> 00:45:06,559
[SPEAKER_09] ipak može i to uzeti u obzir.

526
00:45:06,559 --> 00:45:09,719
[SPEAKER_09] Je li imate osjećaj da razum...

527
00:45:09,719 --> 00:45:12,380
