1087
01:13:23,819 --> 01:13:27,819
[SPEAKER_06] Stoga je regulacija vrlo vjerojatno puno bolja na našoj strani.

1088
01:13:27,819 --> 01:13:32,819
[SPEAKER_06] A čak i kad vam Marin kaže, ali ne, koristimo se samo strogim i dobro reguliranim AI-evima.

1089
01:13:32,819 --> 01:13:37,819
[SPEAKER_06] Uzmite obzir, nikak vam ne dokazuje da ti strogi, jako regulirani AI-evi postoje.

1090
01:13:37,819 --> 01:13:41,819
